                <li><strong>Oct 31:</strong> ITR for taxpayers requiring audit</li>
                <li><strong>Dec 31:</strong> Belated/revised return deadline</li>
                <li>Regime choice can be changed each FY for salaried employees</li>
                <li>Business income: regime lock-in after initial choice</li>
